data.description: Have you ever imagined the perfect blend of country living, enjoying the benefits of county taxes, while still being in close proximity to all your essential amenities? Your dream has found its home here. Step into this captivating residence, where a spacious living room welcomes you with its grandeur and warmth, complete with a delightful gas fireplace that promises cozy evenings.For those who cherish the simple pleasures of life, the covered front porch is a haven of tranquility where you can relish moments of relaxation, soaking in the serene surroundings. Set on an enchanting 1.75 acres of land, this property boasts the soothing presence of a gentle creek that meanders through the back, enhancing the allure of the natural landscape.Unleash your creativity and embrace the abundant space available for your gardening aspirations and hosting memorable gatherings. Car aficionados will delight in the detached 3-car garage, fully equipped with electricity, a haven for both vehicles and hobbies.Venture downstairs and let your imagination run wild within the possibilities of the basement. It's a canvas of potential, ready to be transformed into an additional family retreat, a luxurious in-law haven - plumbing already in place, awaiting your vision.Today is the day to seize this opportunity and transform this property into your personal oasis. Embrace the enchanting country life, relish the convenience of nearby amenities, and create the lifestyle you've been longing for. Your dreams await - make them a reality now!
